  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA39">
<l>iṟaiyāy nilaṉāki yeṇṭicaiyun tāṉāy</l>
<l>maṟaiyāy maṟaipporuḷāy vāṉāyp – piṟaivāynta</l>
<l>veḷḷat taruvi viḷaṅkolinīr vēṅkaṭattā</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷatti ṉuḷḷē yuḷaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As lord, as the land, as the eight directions is he,</l>
<l>as the Veda, the Veda’s meaning, as the sky is he</l>
<l>inside [my] heart, the one from Vēṅkaṭam with roaring water,</l>
<l>shining with waterfalls of a white superior to the crescent moon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
